{"tid":28520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一個政黨　應該有　宣傳部　和　意識形態部 （chenglap）","createTime":"2016-12-08T03:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:31:41.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9efb5155634bc928faa33aac64f23943f76a7c","tid":28520,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10154581075825491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10154581075825491&d=T%2FS5IpksPVt9v4yNcky7FksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=46037b90\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10154581075825491</a><br />\n<br />\n作者 ： Ben Crox<br />\n<br />\n但世事往往不能兼顧，當得了師奶殺手者，偏偏又不容易同時有明確政治意識和雄心。<br />\r\n<br />\n要麼不容易兩者兼備，就是得靠兩種人的合作，去達成政治組織的任務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n一個政黨應該有宣傳部和意識形態部, 這點上說, 我對泛民一定是否定的, 搞了那麼久, 連選議員的人自己對於民主與法治是甚麼都不懂.<br />\r\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n這樣一講，總算明白香港的政黨為何好像欠了甚麼，硬是不太「政黨」。"},{"pid":"2cdcc7eb7527e02e782f0081e7b24b2ee4482af7","tid":28520,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"投机者的意识形态就是投机取巧<br />\n香港社会充斥投机者"},{"pid":"944c2cc2b704707cfb2879fbf2118a783892a7d8","tid":28520,"uid":56187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投机者的意识形态就是投机取巧<br />\n香港社会充斥投机者</blockquote><br />\nblocked"},{"pid":"f0174965c53b46df87c0db1b69efaa71ecd5077a","tid":28520,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"政事台冇人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5cdce6424def0a84695695a1c29dc71f35e9e7","tid":28520,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政事台冇人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係嘅, 始終有意義政治新聞e.g.選舉相關之類唔係日日有, 無意義嘅e.g.大紀元陰謀論, 特首3舊屎再加多舊屎參選, 開到廢事<br />\n<br />\n仲有d post去咗時事台呢"},{"pid":"25d266fb01b8b6686a76f864fb26428f70d67ad9","tid":28520,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政事台冇人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都唔係嘅, 始終有意義政治新聞e.g.選舉相關之類唔係日日有, 無意義嘅e.g.大紀元陰謀論, 特首3舊屎再加多舊屎參選, 開到廢事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有d post去咗時事台呢</blockquote><br />\n新台係咁　ｄ野仲舊就會差唔多　咁不如去舊台<br />\n既然唔係時事台　唔洗個個post都咁即時<br />\n仲可以多ｄ深入長文<br />\n又可以講下意識形態　制度結構　組織發展　戰略分析"},{"pid":"299f6636d7c8063a93962b9d926f494b53722135","tid":28520,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d5eedbc82706854b4a919aed1cfbccd3b388c5","tid":28520,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政事台冇人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都唔係嘅, 始終有意義政治新聞e.g.選舉相關之類唔係日日有, 無意義嘅e.g.大紀元陰謀論, 特首3舊屎再加多舊屎參選, 開到廢事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有d post去咗時事台呢</blockquote><br />\n新台係咁　ｄ野仲舊就會差唔多　咁不如去舊台<br />\n既然唔係時事台　唔洗個個post都咁即時<br />\n仲可以多ｄ深入長文<br />\n又可以講下意識形態　制度結構　組織發展　戰略分析</blockquote><br />\n發達啦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ae009219aefa7757ccff34363517b5e574e030","tid":28520,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}